Katharine McPhee has just signed a record deal with 19 Recordings Ltd , Simon Fullers company and RCA in conjunction with Clive Davis the chairman of BMG USA and RCA Records . 

Katharine McPhee new single will be released on the 27th of June . 

Katharine McPhee was the runner up on the TV hit show American Idol . 

The single will be a double A side , ' Over the Rainbow ' and ' My Desting ' . 

